    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This property defines whether a material is dielectric (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0.0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") or a metallic (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "1.0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "). Although",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "this property can be set to any value between ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "1",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", to create a realistic material, set it",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to either ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "1",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "These are materials that simulate real-world materials that are poor conductors. In these materials, light travels into the surface of the material and the color is mostly controlled by the color of the sub-surface. Typical examples of dielectric materaisl include organic materials, plastics, and industrial minerals such as sand, limestone,  marble, clay and salt.",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Dielectric materials",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "text": "A metallic (or ",
                        "type": "text"
                      },
                      {
                        "inlineContent": [
                          {
                            "text": "conductive",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "emphasis"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": ") material reflects light differently than dielectric ones. The overall color is caused by an immediate re-emission of the light from the entity’s surface. Typical examples of metallic materials include aluminum, chassis metal, chromium, copper, gold, silver, and titanium",
                        "type": "text"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "text": "Metallic",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "type": "termList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
